      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AQUA LILIUM (4) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a P5 at this track over 352m. Key player on best and expected to bounce back. DAINTREE GRACE (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (22.09) at this track behind Spring Graf in a Restricted WIN. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in the finish again. SPRING RORY (2) is better than last start when eighth (22.67) in a Grade 5 at this track over 390m. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Should be in this for a long way. BIZZARO BOY (8) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
